column5: Anyone know where i can get a chart of Jessie lake near Nipigon.  i have been looking high and low.  any help is appreciated.
Not available via Navionics app, check out these guys, they have a lot of area maps and will ship if they have what you need http://www.chaltrek.com/
If it exists, Adam's got it, pm adempsey and see if he can help you out
willing to take a hand drawn sketch at this point.     thanks guys
Is that the Jesse Lake in Quetico PP?  Go to Google Maps and satellite view. Gives you a pretty good idea of what it looks like but no depth or structure.
i hear ya, I do that allot.   no part of the Nipigon river system.   I think I found one thanks guys.
Care to share the info ?  Regards, Snowball
Have you called the the Nipigon area MNR office?
http://www.lineonfishing.com/images/Ontario_Outpost_Lake_Maps/Jessie.pdf  A fellow member hooked me up.
Nice map!  Thanks for posting.  Good luck fishing!  Regards, Snowball
Nice map!  Thanks for posting.  Good luck fishing!  Regards, Snowball  x2 Andrew. Thanks
